OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FA watchdog has called for Winchester
OL,8,Fprison to be put into emergency
OL,9,Fmeasures amid concerns over "very high
OL,10,Flevels of violence" and drug problems.
OL,12,FPrison inspectors wrote to Justice
OL,13,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood to issue an
OL,14,Furgent notification for improvement at
OL,15,Fthe category B jail in Hampshire after
OL,16,F"very poor" inspection findings.
