OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FDrug use was "rife", but the prison's
OL,8,Fapproach to testing was "weak", and a
OL,9,Fthird of CCTV cameras were broken
OL,10,Fwhich "compromised security", the
OL,11,Fwatchdog warned.
OL,13,FSome 41% of the around 690 men held
OL,14,Fthere tested positive for drug use in
OL,15,FAugust, and 47% reported it was easy
OL,16,Fto get hold of illicit substances,
OL,17,Finspectors said.
