OL,7,FThe prison, which also has a lower
OL,8,Fsecurity category C resettlement unit,
OL,9,Fwas so "dilapidated" one inmate had
OL,10,F"been able to remove his own cell
OL,11,Fdoor", the watchdog's inspection
OL,12,Fcarried out earlier this month found.
