OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FDrugs, debt and "prisoner frustration"
OL,8,Fled to the "highest level of serious
OL,9,Fassaults" against staff in all England
OL,10,Fand Wales reception jails ` which
OL,11,Fprocess new inmates into the prison
OL,12,Fsystem and hold people on remand or
OL,13,Fwho have been convicted but yet to be
OL,14,Fsentenced while they are taken to
OL,15,Fcourt.
OL,17,FIt also had the second highest rate
OL,18,Ffor serious assaults against other
OL,19,Finmates, while self-harm was at the
OL,20,Fthird highest level of all prisons of
OL,21,Fthis kind, according to the watchdog.
