OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FMartin Lomas, deputy chief inspector
OL,8,Fof prisons, said: "Winchester was in a
OL,9,Fvery poor state and had been for many
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F"At this most recent inspection we
OL,13,Ffound that standards had deteriorated
OL,14,Fto the point that we had no choice but
OL,15,Fto issue an urgent notification for
OL,16,Fimprovement.
OL,26,@pD@SOUtD@AOU
