OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,F"These very poor outcomes represent
OL,8,Fsystemic failings under the oversight
OL,9,Fof HMPPS (HM Prison and Probation
OL,10,FService) and the Ministry of Justice,
OL,11,Fand will require sustained support and
OL,12,Finvestment if the jail is to provide
OL,13,Fdecent living conditions, keep
OL,14,Fprisoners safe and provide them with
OL,15,Fthe skills they need to succeed in
OL,16,Flife outside prison."
