OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FInspectors also highlighted how
OL,8,Fprisoners were being held in "dreadful
OL,9,Fconditions" with some cells "so damp
OL,10,Fand mouldy that inspectors questioned
OL,11,Fwhether they were fit for habitation."
OL,13,FWinchester is the ninth prison to be
OL,14,Fissued with an urgent notification
OL,15,Fsince November 2022, joining Exeter,
OL,16,FWoodhill, Bristol, Bedford,
OL,17,FWandsworth, Rochester and Manchester
OL,18,Fjails as well as Cookham Wood young
OL,19,Foffender institution. This is the
OL,20,Fsecond warning of its kind the
OL,21,Fwatchdog has made this month.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@KO]qD@]OUsD@fO]
