OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FThe notice effectively places the jail
OL,8,Fin special measures and means the
OL,9,FJustice Secretary has to urgently
OL,10,Fproduce an action plan for improvement
OL,11,Fbefore the watchdog carries out
OL,12,Fanother inspection.
OL,14,FPrisons minister Lord Timpson said:
OL,15,F"This report illustrates the scale of
OL,16,Fthe crisis this Government inherited
OL,17,Fin our prisons.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
