OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,F"Prisons like HMP Winchester must not
OL,8,Fbe allowed to become breeding grounds
OL,9,Ffor further crime. Staff are already
OL,10,Fworking hard to drive the improvements
OL,11,Fneeded and we will publish an action
OL,12,Fplan in the coming weeks to support
OL,13,Fthem in their efforts."
OL,15,FThe full findings of the latest
OL,16,Finspection which prompted the urgent
OL,17,Fnotification will be published at a
OL,18,Flater date.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@WO]
