OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,FThe Howard League for Penal Reform,
OL,8,Fthe oldest penal reform organisation
OL,9,Fin the world, says following the
OL,10,Freport it is time 'to put things
OL,11,Fright'.
OL,13,FChief Executive Andrea Coomber KC,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Winchester is a prison so
OL,15,Fbroken that a man could remove his
OL,16,Fcell door. It has been asked to do too
OL,17,Fmuch, with too little, for too long.
OL,18,FAt the end of last month, it had room
OL,19,Ffor fewer than 450 men ` but it was
OL,20,Fbeing asked to hold more than 600.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
