OL,3,CHampshire prison needs 'urgent
OL,4,Cimprovement' after drug use found to
OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,F"When conditions are so appalling that
OL,8,Fa wall can be prised open with plastic
OL,9,Fcutlery, and when violence, drug use
OL,10,Fand self-harm are rife, what hope is
OL,11,Fthere for the men who spend more than
OL,12,F21 hours each day locked in their
OL,13,Fcells?
OL,26,@oD@AOU
