OL,5,Cbe 'rife'
OL,7,F"There are many other prisons like
OL,8,FWinchester. This is the fourth Urgent
OL,9,FNotification since May, after
OL,10,FWandsworth, Rochester and Manchester,
OL,11,Fand there are likely to be more in the
OL,12,Fnear future. This is why the
OL,13,Fgovernment had no option but to take
OL,14,Femergency measures to ease pressure on
OL,15,Fthe system.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
